====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[break]]; to [[snap]]; to [[cut]]
#: {{zh-x|他 說 他 的 手臂 斷 了。|He said that he'd broken his arm.}}
#: {{zh-x|枝 樹枝 斷{tyun5} 咗。|A tree branch '''broke'''.|C}}
#* {{zh-x|斷 木 為 杵，掘 地 為 臼，臼杵 之 利，萬民 以 濟。|They '''cut''' wood and fashioned it into pestles; they dug in the ground and formed mortars. Thus the myriads of the people received the benefit arising from the use of the pestle and mortar.|ref=Yijing}}
#* {{zh-x|抽 刀 斷 水 水 更 流，舉 杯 銷 愁 愁 更 愁。人生 在世 不 稱{chèn}-意，明朝{zhāo} 散髮 弄 扁{piān}舟。|I take out a knife and '''cut''' the water, but it only flows more violently; I raise my cup to drown my sorrows, but they only intensify. In my life I cannot live in the way I want; tomorrow morning I shall loosen my hair and get on a small boat.|CL|ref=[[s:zh:宣州謝朓樓餞別校書叔雲|宣州謝朓樓餞別校書叔雲]] written by {{w|Li Bai}}}}
# to [[cut off]]; to [[sever]]; to [[interrupt]]
#: {{zh-x|通話 斷 了。|The line has gone dead.}}
#: {{zh-x|斷電|to experience a power outage}}
#: {{zh-x|斷交|to sever ties}}
#* {{zh-x|我 先-后 綏 乃 祖 乃 父，乃 祖 乃 父 乃 斷 棄 汝，不 救 乃 死。|Whereas my royal predecessors made your ancestors and fathers happy, they, your ancestors and fathers, will [now] '''cut''' you '''off''' and abandon you, and not save you from death.|ref=Shujing}}
#* {{zh-x|過言 不 再，流言 不 極；不 斷 其 威，不 習 其 謀。|He does not repeat any error of speech; any rumours against him he does not pursue up to their source; he does not allow his dignity to be '''interrupted'''; he does not dread to practise [beforehand] the counsels [which he gives].|ref=Liji}}
#* {{zh-x|^@蘭芝 初 還{huán} 時，府-吏 見 丁寧，結 誓 不 別離。 今日 違 情義，恐 此 事 非 奇。自 可 斷 來信，徐徐 更 謂 之。|When I came home this time, the clerk pleaded with me again and again, and we made a vow that we'd never part. Today if I went against those feelings, I fear nothing lucky could come of it! Let us '''break off''' these negotiations, or say we need time to think it over slowly.|CL|ref=''{{w|Peacock Flies Southeast|Southeast the Peacock Flies}}'', before 6th century <small>CE</small>, translated by {{w|Burton Watson}}}}
# to [[give up]]; to [[abstain]] from; to [[quit]]
#: {{zh-x|斷 煙|to quit smoking}}
#: {{zh-x|在 孩子 三 個 月 大 時，她 給 孩子 斷 了 奶，並 開始 喂 奶粉。|She [[wean]]ed her baby when he was 3 months old and started him on powdered milk.}}
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to not [[have]]; to be [[without]]; [[there]] is [[not]]

